      "text": "Premium Magnetic Gift Boxes Built for Luxury Presentation & Global Brands"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Magnetic closure gift boxes deliver a premium unboxing experience that elevates any product. Designed with rigid board construction, strong magnets, and luxury printing finishes, these boxes combine durability, elegance, and a high perceived value."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "At Jinhao Xinyuan Group, we manufacture magnetic closure boxes in Vietnam, China, and Thailand, using FSC®-certified papers, precise offset printing, and fully automated rigid box lines for consistent quality."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Whether for cosmetics, apparel, electronics, jewelry, gourmet food, or premium corporate gifting, our magnetic boxes create a strong first impression and protect products throughout the supply chain."
    },
    {
